Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:13.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}確認する 旅団員パクノダ　本人だな？ もちろん。 本当よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:13.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Leol has chased Morel into \Nan underground church, where they will now fight one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:23.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを厳守すれば リーダーは解放する。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:23.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This ability only activates when it rains. Inamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:08.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まずは　リーダーへの条件。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:08.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Return x And x Retire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:15.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１つ　今後　念能力の使用を 一切　禁じる。 ２つ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:15.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My Inamura
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:26.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本当に　これでいいのか？ 奴らの頭さえ潰せば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:26.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well? Aren't my big waves rad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:34.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「クモ」は瓦解する そう思っていた しかし… ((俺に人質としての 価値などない))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:34.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can easily wash away your wimpy smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:44.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}頭をとっても　「クモ」は動く リーダーが絶対なのではない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:44.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You're having trouble moving \Nin the water, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:48.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}場合によっては 頭さえ切り離す集団
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:48.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You like how easily my board can maneuver?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが　「幻影旅団」！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you stand still, I'll give you a quick death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ここでリーダーの動きを 封じたところで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's not your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}奴らを封じることはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It belongs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}かといって 他に　てはあるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to my buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:11.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ない！　見つからない…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:11.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh, making a boat of smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:14.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう　これでいいんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:14.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So he can stand on that smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:24.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}２人を取り戻す それが最優先！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:24.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You think that's enough to defeat my waves? I told you, that's not your ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:37.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう　仲間を失うのは 絶対に嫌だ！ ２つ　今後　旅団員との 一切の接触を絶つこと。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:37.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This one is my own original...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:47.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この律する小指の鎖 「ジャッジメントチェーン」を リーダーに刺す。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:47.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Tornave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}次は　お前だ　パクノダ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I stop my opponent's \Nmovements with a whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１つ　今夜０時までに ゴンとキルアを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Here I go! Then, I finish him with a harpoon from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:28.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}小細工なしで 無事に解放すること。 ２つ　私のことについて 一切　情報を漏らさぬこと。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:28.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My harpoon can match the speed of sound, and pierce a whale at the very bottom \Nof the ocean, even from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}異存がなければ お前にも鎖を刺す。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:44.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もし　ゴンとキルアが　操作系の 能力者に操られているとしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:44.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Impossible! The whirlpool should have incapacitated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:47.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}心音で　それを察知できるか？ 可能よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:47.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He had no way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いつもと　どう違うかは 聞き分けられるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}十分だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:00.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}人質交換の前に 言っておくことがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:00.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I simply exhaled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:04.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}When it comes to lung capacity, \Nno one in the world beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:13.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あなたは頭の隅で 矛盾を感じている パクノダが　なぜ１人で来たのか そのことに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:13.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He used his breath as jet propulsion \Nto break out of the whirlpool?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:17.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「旅団」が本当に 非情なだけの組織なら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:17.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, it's my turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}この人質交換自体 成立しないはず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:21.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's your turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((追い詰められているのは お前達のほうだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}In this battle, you don't get a turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}彼らは　鉄の掟を作り
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:27.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}All you get to do is drown in my waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:32.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団長は　それを 順守しようとしている でも　団員は？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:32.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}During this exchange, I've learned three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}少なくとも彼女は違う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:35.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}First, I now know your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:42.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あなたが憎しみを 絞り出すようにしながら 見据えている　その女性は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:42.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Somehow, you're able to use \Nother people's abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:47.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今　あなたと同じ理由で そこに立っているのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:47.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And those earphones have nothing to do with your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:49.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ただ　仲間を…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:49.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They're either for show or for luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:53.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団長を救いたい一心で…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:53.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Or it means someone is sending you orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:06:04.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あなたは　それに 気づいているのでしょ？ まず　お前は仲間の元に戻り 人質交換の旨を伝える。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:06:04.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If he meant to impair his hearing \Nto strengthen his power, he shouldn't be able to hear me talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:08.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そして　０時までに２人を連れて リンゴーン空港に来い。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:08.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What's the third thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:12.24,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仲間は連れて来るな どこに行くかも言うな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:12.24,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your lifespan. That Inamura ability belongs \Nto a Hunter named Grachan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:18.74,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分かったわ　交渉成立ね 空港へ送ってちょうだい。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:18.74,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You probably encountered and defeated \Nhim when he was sent
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:24.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なぜ　何も聞かない。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:24.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll punish you for stealing my buddy's ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:29.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私が何者か分かってるんだろう？ 不安じゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:29.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your life ends today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}理不尽な交渉だと思わないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:32.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hold on... That's a totally one-sided misinterpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:35.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私が本当に リーダーを返すと思うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:35.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I was protecting myself from humans \Nwho were hunting me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ええ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It was self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:43.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あなたに　だます気があるなら わざわざ そんなこと聞かないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:43.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And I didn't steal his ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:54.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}のめると思ってるのか そんな条件をよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:54.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's an excuse thieves use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}場所を言え　パクノダ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, arguing with you is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:04.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ガキ２人を殺して 鎖野郎をやりに行く。 どうしても？ どうしてもだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:04.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'd like to get my hands on his ability, but defeating him is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:12.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}言わないなら 行かせるわけにはいかねえ。 絶対に場所は言わないし ２人を連れて戻るのは私だけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:12.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Right now, our top priority \Nis to defeat one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}邪魔しないで。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll repeat myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:17.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}邪魔!?　そりゃ　どっちの話だよ コラ　あ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:17.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm sorry, but you don't get a turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:25.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}行きなよ　パクノダ ここは　あたし達が止める。 止める？　ナメてるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:25.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Big Wall! Giant Wave\NBig Wall
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.67,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前ら　頭どうかしちまったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.67,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm flooding this underground church. My wall of water's gonna suck you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:36.25,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}恐らく　私達　着く前に 全員　鎖野郎にやられてるね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:36.25,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Just try and find your way to the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:46.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本当に分からないの？ あ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:46.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Now, will he make it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:51.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パクノダが　なぜ　お前達に何も話さず 戻ろうとしているのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:51.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Will I smash his skull with my board? Launch my harpoon through his gut?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:54.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}マチが　なぜ　お前達を 止めようとしているのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:54.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Which do I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:08:01.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}本当に操られてるからって 思ってんの!? お前達の団長を助けたいからに 決まってるだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:08:01.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Either way, if he shows his face above water, he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:09.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}仲間を取り戻したいって気持が そんなに理解できないのか！ 黙ってろ　ガキが！ 助かりたくって必死か？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:09.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}He isn't coming back up... Has he drowned?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:16.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}自分のために 言ってるんじゃ　ない。 取り消せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:16.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, he was confident about his lung capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}やれやれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That means he can survive for \Nten or twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:23.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}嫌なこった 文句あるなら来いよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.15,0:08:23.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, wait. It's just possible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:29.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}一歩でも動いたら その首　へし折るぜ。 じゃ　嫌だね！　誰が動くもんか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:29.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}that he's able to remain underwater like a whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もしも お前達と約束を交わしたのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:43.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それを一方的に破ることも 絶対しない！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:43.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それは　直接会ったパクノダには 分かったはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll impale you with my harpoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:50.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}条件通りにすれば 団長は必ず戻って来る！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:50.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Bubbles on the opposite side, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:54.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}勝手なこと ゴチャゴチャ吹きやがって！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:54.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And over here! And over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.17,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もう　やめろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:57.17,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There are air bubbles everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:06.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}シャル　今　俺達にとって 最悪のケースってのは　何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:06.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's possible, if he formed his smoke \Ninto a hose with multiple branches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん… 団長が　すでに死んでて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That way, he wouldn't give away his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パクノダ達が操作されている。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hey! How long are you gonna stay under?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:18.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}鎖野郎の所在は　結局　知れず この２人にも まんまと逃げられる…　かな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:18.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Do you expect me to give up and drain the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それが間違ってんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No, that isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最悪なのは　俺達全員がやられて 「クモ」が死ぬことだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The bubbles are camouflage! Is he running?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:30.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それに比べりゃ お前が言ったケースなんざ 屁みてぇなもんだ　違うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:30.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If his lung capacity is that great, it's possible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ん…　まぁ　そうだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}he could swim out through the maze of \Nunderground corridors leading down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:37.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}理由はどうであれ　お前ら どっちも団長に　より過ぎだぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:37.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I can't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:44.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その結果 「旅団」が致命的に崩壊してみろ。 それが団長に対する 一番の裏切りだろうが。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:44.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I told Welfin and Brovada to stay out of this, \Nso I could take all the credit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:49.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}このまま　もめてたら そうなりかねねえぞ　頭冷やせ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:49.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My head's spinning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}いいじゃねえか　好きにさせて。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}And my chest hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:55.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ガキとパクノダを行かせて もし団長が戻って来なかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:55.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Have I been poisoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}簡単なことだろうが。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My board disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:05.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それでいいよ それで気が済むならね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:05.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Is it because my physical and \Nmental stability are compromised?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:09.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まぁ　あたしゃ操られてないし 簡単に　やられもしないけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:09.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チッ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:16.70,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL] もしもし。 [TEL]　人質の２人に代われ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:16.70,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}My power stopped working, \Nbut the water hasn't gone away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.21,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}壊すなよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.21,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because we're underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:20.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　大丈夫か？　奴らは　いるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:20.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:24.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　全員いるよ。 おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:24.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I let him think he had the advantage \Nso I could turn the tables on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:28.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}チッ…　そっちの条件通り…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:28.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it looks as though the one \Nwho was backed into a corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:34.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}追わなくていいのか？ これで　もう鎖野郎が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:34.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:42.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うるせぇ　追おうとすりゃ また　お前らが止めるだろうが。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:42.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Am I gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:50.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}とりあえず　様子見ててやるよ。 もし　これで団長が 戻って来なかったら てめぇも　ぶっ殺すからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:50.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Am I... Am I gonna die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:58.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　止まっている飛行船に乗れ 行き先は　もう伝えてある。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:58.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So he was using smoke hoses
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:01.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}約束通り　３人ね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:01.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to send air bubbles everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:05.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}飛び立つまでは分からない 周りを注意してくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:05.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But what kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.20,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あっちから人が来る！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.20,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}poison did he use?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That was faster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:14.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あれは！　ヒソカ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:14.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The poison you've inhaled is lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　やぁ。 何で来たのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But it's something naturally found in air.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:23.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　抜け出して来たのか!? 安心しなよ 影武者を置いて来ているから。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:23.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Carbon dioxide. Morel used his immense lung capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:33.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}針なしで顔変えると　４５時間で 元に戻っちゃうから… [TEL]　何をたくらんでる？ 僕も　こいつに乗せてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:33.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}to suck in the stagnant air trapped in the church, and exhaled it with an increased \Nconcentration of carbon dioxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:37.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}断ったら　この場で ゴンとキルアを殺しちゃうかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:37.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I started my attack
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:43.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}[TEL]　貴様…！ なんて…　そんな もったいないことしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:43.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}before you ever began.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:50.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}僕のターゲットは　団長のみ。 彼が解放されれば 僕も船を降りるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:50.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If he was telling the truth, Grachan should be getting his ability back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}キルア　ケータイを胸に当てろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I have a few hours in which to move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大丈夫　何もされてないわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}During that time, I must see \Nthem with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}よし！　交換開始だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've observed Bizeff's movements \Nwith my crystal ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}存分に味わうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:54.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:56.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}出発していいそうだ。 そう。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:56.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:41.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうそう 実は　僕の本当の占いでは 団長とのデートは 火曜日のはずで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:41.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh? How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:47.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団員は半分になってる はずだったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:47.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Octopus! Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:51.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}運命は　少しずつ　ずれて来ている。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:51.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How long was I out? Don't call me an octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:58.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ううん　団長に鎖を刺せたんだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:58.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is an underground clinic for folks \Nwith roots in the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:03.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ああ　だが　これで 全てが解決したわけではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:03.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You were out for two whole days. Two days?! I need to get going! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ニャ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You need a few days before— Oh, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:23.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団長は？ ここには来られない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:23.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's great. Thanks for everything you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:26.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あ!?　ふざけろよ きっちり説明しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:26.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm checking out now. Not until you pay me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}返答次第じゃ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Your total bill comes to 1.8 million Jenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:33.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}大丈夫　その代わり…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:33.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}If you can't pay, I'll take body parts instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１度に撃てる弾は６発
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't have my wallet on me. \NI'll wire it to you when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ちょうど　結成時のメンバー分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm not stupid enough to trust \Nthat you'll keep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:46.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フェイタン　フィンクス マチ　ノブナガ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:46.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Until you find someone to bring \Nthe money, you're staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}シャルナーク　フランクリン。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:49.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:56.72,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}信じて　受け止めてくれる？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:56.72,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It costs 10,000 Jenny per minute. Would you just shut up and go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まさか…　パク！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Hello? Hey, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:04.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}おい！ お前　やっぱり奴に操作され…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:04.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Killua! Where are you? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}フィンクス！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:09.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}信じろ　あれはパクだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:09.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll explain when I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:16.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私の記憶　私の思い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:16.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A strong enemy gave me some trouble. I've been in the hospital. Oh... Well, I'm glad you called. This means you're okay now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:20.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全て込める
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:20.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, I'll be back soon. Anything happen on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:31.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:31.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We have a plan that could \Ndefeat the King if it goes well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お願い…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:38.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}私で…　終わりに…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:38.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We should meet, so I can hear what you think. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パク…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Then, I need you to send money \Nto a certain bank account.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:49.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}死んでる…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:49.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That just leaves Palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:51.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どういうこと？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:51.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You haven't been able to reach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺が説明する。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:53.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No. She's probably still in the palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}全て分かった。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But wouldn't that mean Neferpitou's \NNen has already exposed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パクノダは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I imagine she's in the warehouse, \Nbeneath the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:15.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカの熱 このまま下がらないといいのにね。 そうだな。 …って　おい！ 今　すごいこと言っただろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:15.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Pitou's En can't reach that far. But since the exit is in the \Npalace, she can't get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:19.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカは　もう　「旅団」と 闘っちゃダメな気がするんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:19.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}How's Knov-san doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:25.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}クラピカから能力のこと聞いた時 思ったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:25.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}he's probably out of this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:32.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}もっと別の能力に してたんじゃないかって。 そうかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:32.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But he did manage to place the exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:35.69,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だって 本当に相手を殺そうと思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:35.69,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}There's no change to our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:39.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}心臓に鎖を打ち込むなんて 回りくどいやり方しないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:39.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Three days to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:52.12,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}１人　捕まえても すぐには殺せないよ。 他の仲間のこととか 聞かなきゃなんないしさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:52.12,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}His wounds are already healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そっか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:06.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}でも最初は　そうだったとしても 今のクラピカは　もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:06.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Okay, I confirmed receipt of the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:10.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13})
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:10.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}You can leave. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:23.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}団長が戻らなきゃ 奴ら　今まで以上に 必死でクラピカ捜すだろうし。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:23.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What are you doing? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:24.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}俺達も オークション会場に行く時は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}We're gonna join my buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:29.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}細心の注意を払わないと。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:29.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.68,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}『グリードアイランド』に関する 秘策ってのはよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:33.68,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:39.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お前の作戦頼みなんだぞ！ うん…　でも　確率は五分五分だよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.68,0:18:39.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Well, I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:42.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}最初　７０％とか 言ってなかったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:42.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'll just tell you this. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}なるほど　そりゃ面白い。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Uh, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:48.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}…っていうか それしかないって感じだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:48.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:51.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}現実的で　かつ堅実。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:51.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's okay if I come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:55.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}うん　五分五分どころか ８割方　成功する！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:55.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I mean, I'm just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.19,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}ホント!? ああ　行けるぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.19,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.63,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}オークション会場は Ｂホールだって。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.63,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Was I the only one who thought \Nwe were already friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}お！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It's really... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}えっ？ えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It isn't about what's okay. It's whether you're coming or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:19.18,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}何で奴らが　ここにいんのさ!? 知るかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:19.18,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I'm going! I'm going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}逃げるっつうの！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I want to make something clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:29.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}安心するね 別に　お前達やるつもりないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:29.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The next time something like this happens, I won't bother thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:38.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今となったら鎖野郎を やるわけにもいかなくなったしな。 えっ　どういうこと？ あぁ？ 団長に「念」の鎖　刺したんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:38.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}So if something happens, \Nand I end up helping you, you don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:43.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}じゃあ 殺せるわけねえじゃねぇか。 何で？　逆じゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:43.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Friends are supposed to help friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:48.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}こういう時　便利だよなぁ 素直に聞ける　こいつの性格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:48.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}From now on, we'll be working together. So we'll be helping each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:52.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}「念」ってのは　死ねば消えるとは 限らねえんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:52.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Supporting each other isn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:58.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}深い恨みや 未練を持ったまま死ぬと その「念」は　強く残る。 残された「念」は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:58.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}It'd be lame to thank each other \Nfor every little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:02.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}憎悪や執着の対象へ おのずと向かう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:02.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Yeah, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そうなると 念能力を使えねえ団長は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}This is the world I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:09.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}その邪念を　もろに受けて 心身をやられちまう恐れがある。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:09.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The world I longed for and sought...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:12.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}それほど　死者の「念」は強い。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:12.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}But deep down, I thought \Nit was beyond my reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:15.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}だから　鎖野郎をやるわけには…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:15.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That it wasn't meant for me... \NAnd wouldn't happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:22.66,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}分かってるよ これ以上　言わねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:22.66,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I thought it wasn't meant to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:29.16,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}除去できる者がいる ってことはな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:29.16,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Killua, I'm... I'm so happy, I could die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.62,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}東か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.62,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Huh? Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:38.71,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}まっ　そんなわけで　俺達は お前らから手を引く。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:38.71,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Because... Because you're doing this for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:42.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}今日は　純粋に 競売を楽しみに来ただけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:42.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:45.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}他の連中は ホームに戻る気だしな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:45.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I want to make one more thing clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:49.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あの…　パクノダさんは？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:49.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}The world you're stepping into is far more brutal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}あいつは死んだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}than the world of the Chimera Ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}そう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}They may seem similar, but there's a huge difference between \Nrisking a life and throwing it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:04.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((手負いの私からなら 逃げられるはずでしょ))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:04.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}People staring death in the face every day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.64,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((そしたら　こっちの切り札は なくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.64,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}don't want to hear that someone's ready to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:16.15,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}鎖野郎は　望み通り 団長を殺せるのに 何で　そうしないの？ あいつの仲間なんでしょ？)) )
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:16.15,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Only people who maintain a daily \Nregimen to stay in tip-top shape, and can swallow just enough poison to \Nfall short of a lethal dose, get to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:20.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((仲間だから　本当はクラピカに 人殺しなんてしてほしくない))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:20.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}That's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:24.73,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}((だから　交換で済むなら それが一番いいんだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:24.73,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}Are you ready to join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:32.14,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}どうしたの？ 早く行こうぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:32.14,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}the words I most wanted to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:39.65,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}パクは　お前らに感謝してたぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:39.65,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}A foolish question. I see paradise before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}次回　物語は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've seen the other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:51.13,Subs1,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}グリードアイランド編へと 動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:51.13,Subs2,NA,0,0,0,,{\be13}I've made contact.
